description: This table presents the link prediction results of several TKGR methods and LLMs-based TKGR methods on two datasets, ICEWS14 and ICEWS05-15.  The performance is evaluated using Mean Reciprocal Rank (MRR) and Hit@N (N=1,3,10) metrics. LLM-DA, a novel method proposed in the paper, is compared with traditional methods and other LLM-based methods. The table highlights the performance improvements of LLM-DA by showing that it achieves the best results in most cases, even without fine-tuning the LLMs.
